      "comment": "OH SWEET CREATURE (9) did a good job for a 2m third in a higher-graded race at Maryborough last start and scored the last time he raced here, taking his record at the circuit to two wins and a placing from three attempts. Also owns a good record at the distance and draws for a nice trail. MIKI LOCH (7) draws wide but came from one spot deeper when he won here earlier in the month and has been close-up since including a 1.7m second last week. LE BETTY (5) draws lower than in the last-start fourth and strikes at 50 per cent at this venue including a win the only time she attempted this distance here. ASTRAL STRIDE (2) will be race fit now and looks a big improver from this draw.",
